Subject: AIC displaying SIDs not User Names
Description:
Hello,

We just noticed what appears to be an issue with how the AIC is displaying Activity Events. It used to be it would show the names of the users, but now it only shows the SID of the user.
DevOps_Steps_to_Reproduce__c:
Log in to AIC
Click on Resource Audit
Expand SharePoint
Look for Activity Details
I explained to the customer that he needed an Azure license to retrieve details about the user's login information.
What_We_Know__c: The customer was looking for information on the Azure domain, but he's not licensed for Azure.
Solution_Comment__c: I explained to the customer that he needs an Azure license to use the application to collect information from the Azure site.
